node.hospital_zh: 東區尤德夫人那打素醫院
node.detail_zh: 患者過往健康良好，2 月 22 日至7 月 4 日曾到巴基斯坦，抵港後由檢疫中心送院，沒有病徵，與第 #1274 宗個案患者有關連。
node.detail_en: The patient has good past health, was in Pakistan between February 22 and July 4, and was hospitalised from quarantine centre upon return to Hong Kong, having exhibited no symptoms. Her case has epidemiological links with that of patient #1274.
